vdcEye onvifmanager
open source ONVIF IP Camera manager

Please Delete C:\videodb if use vdcEye Manager V2014-0630.msi and before.

vdcEye Manager which support recording and unlimited timeline playback
https://sourceforge.net/projects/vscloud/

ONVIF profile S support.
Unlimited timeline playback.
Anti file system fragment recording system.
Multi Display screen support.
Alarm Support
PTZ Support
ONVIF ProfileS simulator
Mobile Support (TODO)
Profile G Support (TODO)

Windows Build:
1. Install VS2013
2. Install QT 5.4.0 in the http://download.qt-project.org/official_releases/qt/5.2/5.2.1/qt-opensource-windows-x86-msvc2010-5.2.1.exe
3. http://download.qt-project.org/official_releases/vsaddin/qt-vs-addin-1.2.3-opensource.exe 
4. Open the vepro\prj_win32\VSCloudNode.sln to build

Linux Build:
ubuntu: sudo apt-get install libx11-dev yasm libxext-dev libgl1-mesa-dev  zlib1g-dev
centos: sudo yum install nasm xorg-x11-server-devel zlib-devel

1. Install qt-opensource-linux-x64-5.4.0.run
	export  PATH=$PATH:/home/ubu/Qt5.2.1/5.2.1/gcc_64/bin:/home/ubu/Qt5.2.1/Tools/QtCreator/bin/
	
